{"tid":563971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上片段顯示有人自行燃放煙花　警方稱市民可舉報","createTime":"2018-02-17T12:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T13:23:48.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"509b42500105e7c469e03a80c6944f2358821663","tid":563971,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"有市民上載到網上的片段，由前日至今日凌晨期間，本港多區包括深水埗﹑屯門大興邨﹑大埔林村河等，懷疑有市民自行燃放煙花。警方回覆說，市民如懷疑有人進行違法活動，可向警方舉報。<br />\n<br />\n至於有無處理以上個案，警方未有回應，但強調致力打擊非法藏有及燃放煙花爆竹的違法行為，任何人非法藏有或燃放煙花爆竹，均屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1381349-20180217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1381349-20180217.htm&d=u16ti%2BQKRfEP63qtE5Xr1HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6754b8b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1381349-20180217.htm&h=bad1df9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1381349-20180217.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f771d81ed1ebaa924c1b6b1c74584e7a7e769d90","tid":563971,"uid":20448,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T12:51:37.000Z","msg":"大陸放得點解香港唔放得啊<br />\n成班差佬係咪支持港獨啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"b93599795871f59e74d287b3dc082b45c770fde7","tid":563971,"uid":90577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T12:51:38.000Z","msg":"住太子,頭先出面有砰砰炮杖聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26530ff76cb1057fef61e062a10cff331cc7060b","tid":563971,"uid":54733,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"警犬對住牛屎佬就龜縮架啦<br />\n<br />\n舉報完會夠膽入村?"},{"pid":"44758fe5dcaa44211b6d5d85a0529ffaa6da09d5","tid":563971,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"26530ff76cb1057fef61e062a10cff331cc7060b","tid":563971,"uid":54733,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17